## Deep Extensive Imaging of Person in Pain (DEIPP) dataset

This dataset contains the raw MRI data for the following reference:

Jae-Joong Lee, Seongwoo Jo, Sungkun Cho, Choong-Wan Woo, Personalized Brain Decoding of Spontaneous Pain in Individuals With Chronic Pain, in revision

For more information about preprocessing and analysis code accompanying the data, please visit the following repository: [https://github.com/cocoanlab/DEIPP](https://github.com/cocoanlab/DEIPP)
